25 LC 112 3211
House Resolution 474
By: Representative Hagan of the 156th
A RESOLUTION
1 Congratulating the Toombs County High School football team for winning the 2024 GHSA
2 Class A Division 1 State Football Championship; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, the Toombs County High School football team has established and maintained
4 a proud tradition of excellence with equal emphases on character and academics; and
5 WHEREAS, this superlative team has completed another triumphant season of football
6 competition by posting an outstanding record of 13 wins and only one loss; and
7 WHEREAS, excellent play, superior teamwork, and extraordinary resilience made this team
8 a spectacular one to observe throughout the season, and as a fitting finale to its remarkable
9 2024 campaign, the team captured its first ever state football championship; and
10 WHEREAS, the team brought special recognition to its school and to Toombs County by
11 winning the 2024 GHSA Class A Division 1 State Football Championship against Northeast
12 High School with a final score of 38-18; and
