13 WHEREAS, the phenomenal performance of the team is a clear indication of the outstanding
14 athletic ability, dedication, hard work, and unity of purpose and spirit of each member of the
15 team; and
16 WHEREAS, this magnificent team performed with precision during the season and earned
17 its well-deserved reputation for high standards of athletic achievement, the quality of its play,
18 and the stiff competition it presented to its opponents.
19 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
20 the members of this body congratulate the Toombs County High School football team for
21 winning the 2024 GHSA Class A Division 1 State Football Championship and extend best
22 wishes for continued success.
23 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
24 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the
25 Toombs County High School football team.
